    {
      "instruction": "<p>Decrease the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>onion wedges</strong>, <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the dish</p><p>Add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground paprika</strong> and<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
